      "span_text": "Similar, putative Zfh1 homeodomain binding sites corresponding to the degenerate sequence CTAATYRRNTT used to identify the eve RCSI-like motif  were indeed significantly enriched in Zfh1 DamID peaks from both S2 cells (PWMenrich raw score 1.377; p=8.06 E-11) and CySCs (raw score 1.421; p=1.377 E-07) (Stojnic, R. and Diez, D. (2015) .",
